<sect2>
<title>Installation de libxml2</title>

<para>Installez <application>libxml2</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</userinput></screen>

